content.body:
Maybe something along the lines of `Request.json("https://example.org", body, { method: "POST" })` as alternative to

```js
new Request("https://example.org", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json; charset=utf-8",
  },
  body: JSON.stringify(body),
})
```

